{"word":"G4483 - ῥέω - rhéō - hreh'-o - Command","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ῥέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">rhéō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">hreh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Command</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - உரை, சொல், உத்தரவு கொடு"},{"paragraph":"to flow"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>For certain tenses of which a prolonged form (<b>&#x03B5;&#x0313;&#x03C1;&#x03B5;&#x0301;&#x03C9;</b> <b>ereo&#x0304;</b>) is used; and both as alternate for <a href=\"#/G2036 - ἔπω - épō - ep'-o/2036\">G2036</a>; perhaps akin (or identical) with <a href=\"#/G4482 - ῥέω - rhéō - hreh'-o/4482\">G4482</a> (through the idea of <i>pouring</i> forth); to <i>utter</i>, that is, <i>speak</i> or <i>say</i>: - command, make, say, speak (of). Compare <a href=\"#/G3004 - λέγω - légō - leg'-o/3004\">G3004</a>.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}